rComments: He's decent. He is unclear of what he wants his students to do in the course. He can be funny at times but there are times where his class feels like a grade nine french class. There are not many students so his classes are more personal but it is still not the best class I've ever taken. The content is easy though.
Lectures weren't interesting nor were they helpful... he doesn't answer his emails and his expectations weren't clear. I've taken several FLS courses and this was my least favorite by far.
